shortDescription.default: This web part fetches all the automatically added header anchor tags in a SharePoint page and displays them in a navigation component.

longDescription.default: This web part fetches all the automatically added header anchor tags in a SharePoint page and displays them in a navigation component. When added to a vertical section it can be used as a contents table for the page.

features.title: Page navigator
features.description: The feature that activates elements of the navigator solution.
